OL,3,C77% of homeowners 'think EPC rating
OL,4,Cwill be important when moving home'
OL,6,FMore than three-quarters (77%) of
OL,7,Fhomeowners feel that an EPC (energy
OL,8,Fperformance certificate) rating will
OL,9,Fbe important when choosing a property
OL,10,Fto buy in the future, according to
OL,11,Fresearch for Britain's biggest
OL,12,Fbuilding society.
OL,14,FA similar proportion (78%) of
OL,15,Fhomeowners expect buyers to pay more
OL,16,Ffor an energy efficient home,
OL,17,FNationwide Building Society said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
