CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782436704
OL,3,C77% of homeowners 'think EPC rating
OL,4,Cwill be important when moving home'
OL,6,FNearly a third (32%) of people aged 25
OL,7,Fto 34 years old expect buyers to pay
OL,8,Fsignificantly more for an energy
OL,9,Fefficient home, compared with just 5%
OL,10,Fof those aged 55-plus.
OL,12,FNationwide also found that 69% of
OL,13,Fhomeowners believe that EPC ratings
OL,14,Fand energy efficiency matter more now
OL,15,Fthan when they bought their home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
