CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782436704
OL,3,C77% of homeowners 'think EPC rating
OL,4,Cwill be important when moving home'
OL,6,FDespite this, more than half (54%) of
OL,7,Fthose surveyed were not aware of their
OL,8,Fcurrent property's energy efficiency
OL,9,Frating, according to the survey of
OL,10,Fmore then 2,000 homeowners carried out
OL,11,Fby Censuswide in May.
OL,13,FOf homeowners who had undertaken
OL,14,Fmeasures to improve their home's
OL,15,Fenergy efficiency in the past 10
OL,16,Fyears, the most popular were adding
OL,17,Fsolar panels, improving insulation and
OL,18,Fupgrading to energy-saving windows and
OL,19,Fdoors, the survey across the UK found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
