PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782436704
OL,3,C77% of homeowners 'think EPC rating
OL,4,Cwill be important when moving home'
OL,6,FAndrew Harvey, Nationwide's senior
OL,7,Feconomist, said: "The main reasons
OL,8,Fcited for making green improvements
OL,9,Fwere to reduce energy bills and to
OL,10,Fmake their home more comfortable.
OL,12,F"Nearly three-quarters (73%) said they
OL,13,Fhad seen energy bills fall as a result
OL,14,Fof the improvements they made."
OL,16,FSome 77% also said they were more
OL,17,Flikely to remain in their current
OL,18,Fproperty longer as a result of the
OL,19,Fimprovements they had made.
OL,26,@oD@ROUtD@AOUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
