FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782436704
OL,3,C77% of homeowners 'think EPC rating
OL,4,Cwill be important when moving home'
OL,6,FOf who have not made green
OL,7,Fimprovements, the most commonly cited
OL,8,Freason is they cannot afford the
OL,9,Fupfront cost.
OL,11,FNationwide calculated that, in
OL,12,FEngland, an owner-occupied home rated
OL,13,FA or B attracts a 1.6% house price
OL,14,Fpremium compared with a D-rated home,
OL,15,Flooking at properties where an EPC was
OL,16,Favailable.
OL,18,FDavid Fell, lead analyst at Hamptons,
OL,19,Fsaid: "Rising energy bills have made
OL,20,Fbuyers keener than ever to understand
OL,21,Fhow much it costs to run a home.
OL,26,@{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
