PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1782436704
OL,3,C77% of homeowners 'think EPC rating
OL,4,Cwill be important when moving home'
OL,6,F"Buyers increasingly look for a
OL,7,Fminimum of an EPC C rating, which
OL,8,Ftypically means the basics have all
OL,9,Fbeen done: the home is well-insulated,
OL,10,Fhas a modern boiler, and double
OL,11,Fglazing.
OL,13,F"If homes don't offer this, buyers are
OL,14,Flooking to factor in the costs
OL,15,Frequired to achieve it."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@XO]
